{
  "stem": "9590.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I just saw around me some other children that weren't so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Their families were poor, and they could not afford the things that we had, for instance, a bicycle, or ice skating, or even books from school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I went to public school in that shtetl, Warkowicze.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was a good student and conscientious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I took advantage of the library.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I loved to read.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And less fortunate children that did not have books came to me, and I gladly shared with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Life was that way 'til I graduated the public school, six years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that, I prepared for exams to enter high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We called it gimnazjum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was very, very prestigious [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for a girl from a small town to go to a bigger city and enter a gimnazjum, and I was thankful that my parents provided that possibility for me.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That summer, I prepared for the exams.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then I passed the exams in flying colors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And in 1939, my parents brought me to Rowne, and I entered the gimnazjum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was a wonderful experience for a young girl to-- to see a much broader world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Those were my early teens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met some wonderful children from different cities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I was a shy girl, but the atmosphere appealed to me very, very much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I had a curious mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I wanted to learn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The [NON-ENGLISH] of the gimnazjum was very high.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The requirements were big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But I didn't mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I was studious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We learned languages, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I learned English, which in my wildest fantasy I couldn't believe that I will ever have to use it as my main language.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We learned Latin.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
